<plot>Unni is a little boy who lives in a village at Kerala. He belongs to the superior caste of Nairs. His friends Raju, Ramu and Gopi, who go to school with him, belong to the lowest caste of all. The film is the first in the trilogy Life Is All About Friends and deals with the relationship between these children and the discoveries they make together concerning the world about them.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?631357</url></doc>
